Package org.dapper.ui

A package for a simple Dapper user interface.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CodeletTree
    A visual hierarchy of Dapper execution archives and their Codelets.
    CodeletTree.RunnableNode
    A subclass of DefaultMutableTreeNode that contains runnable code.
    FlowBuilderDialog
    A subclass of JDialog for aiding in the creation of command-line arguments for FlowBuilder instantiation.
    FlowManager
    A visual manager for Dapper Flows.
    FlowManagerDriver
    A driver class for FlowManager.
    FlowPane
    A subclass of JTabbedPane that serves as an index of FlowTabs.
    FlowTab
    A subclass of JLabel associated with Flow information.
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    Program
    An annotation that specifies the Codelet class names upon which a program depends.
